00:22:54.640 --> 00:22:58.640
but that ability did not exist in Connect before today.

00:22:58.640 --> 00:23:05.640
So now that Connect can kind of inherit those row-level permissions,

00:23:05.640 --> 00:23:10.640
it gives you the ability to have that same experience that you have in Workbench in Connect.

00:23:16.640 --> 00:23:25.640
